<br>
You suggest to me ideas. The point of this is to have Polykarbon members' characters and storylines featured on the cards. You can do fan art, but only of other polykarbon member's stuff. I will not accept ideas based on works that already exist. This is to keep the focus of the cards on Polykarbon rather that having people submit stuff only from their favorite anime or book.<br>
<br>
That way, you can be inspired to work on your characters and storylines, and on the side have them appear in cards.<br>
<br>
Therefor, please form your ideas and send them to my email address, where i can quickly and organizedly process your card submissions. you may post the ideas here if you want, but it will be easier for me if i get them via email.<br>
<br>
I am doing this by submission to be respectful of people's copyrights. I could very well cruise the art board and save copies of all the pictures and do it that way, but someone would be offended and then the aspect of involvement is lost. I took liberties with Traum4 because i needed an example, i was confident that he would be gracious about it.<br>
<br>
So get your ideas in, and once i make your artist card you can start getting character cards done. Then you can use them however you want, on your personal icon or signiture, or toss them into your other fight clubs for fun, or put them on your website. thats cool with me, as long as you provide a link maybe back to this thread (or if i had a website, any help on that would be great). <p><BR>
